[
  {
    "startTime": 2.435,
    "endTime": 4.6370000000000005,
    "text": "♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.637,
    "endTime": 5.271,
    "text": "[gasp]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.271,
    "endTime": 7.673,
    "text": "Hey! Whoa! I got it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.674,
    "endTime": 9.376000000000001,
    "text": "Hey, your groceries are really heavy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.376,
    "endTime": 11.177,
    "text": "You'd better let me carry these for ya."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.177,
    "endTime": 13.379,
    "text": "You know I'm not always saving the universe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.38,
    "endTime": 15.915000000000001,
    "text": "Sometimes it's just about helping ordinary people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.915,
    "endTime": 17.416,
    "text": "I learned that from my friend, Thor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.417,
    "endTime": 19.919,
    "text": "♪ [carnival music] ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.919,
    "endTime": 22.655,
    "text": "C'mon Spidey, ring the bell, win a prize."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.655,
    "endTime": 23.89,
    "text": "[thud]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.89,
    "endTime": 24.791,
    "text": "[ding]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.791,
    "endTime": 26.292,
    "text": "Hah! Beat that Thor!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.292,
    "endTime": 27.360000000000003,
    "text": "With pleasure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.295,
    "endTime": 30.163,
    "text": "[clang]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.163,
    "endTime": 31.731,
    "text": "Nice work, Thor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.731,
    "endTime": 32.332,
    "text": "[shivering]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.731,
    "endTime": 32.332,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.401,
    "endTime": 36.336000000000006,
    "text": "Ugh. Snow when it's this hot?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.336,
    "endTime": 38.638,
    "text": "I'm no meteorologist but this isn't normal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.638,
    "endTime": 41.207,
    "text": "Aye, the foul weather is unnatural!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.207,
    "endTime": 42.776,
    "text": "And I see who is responsible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.776,
    "endTime": 44.277,
    "text": "My evil brother, Loki."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.277,
    "endTime": 48.415,
    "text": "Spider-man, Thor, and the humans having fun in the sun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.415,
    "endTime": 52.986,
    "text": "Bah! Since I've always despised you super heroes and you humans,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.986,
    "endTime": 57.123,
    "text": "I'll have a good time ruining everyone's summer fun!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.123,
    "endTime": 58.291,
    "text": "[evil Laugh]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.291,
    "endTime": 59.793,
    "text": "Leave the people alone!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.861,
    "endTime": 63.663,
    "text": "Yeah, Loki! Quit with the cold."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.663,
    "endTime": 65.197,
    "text": "When I'm through with all of you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.197,
    "endTime": 66.598,
    "text": "you won't just be cold;"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.599,
    "endTime": 67.7,
    "text": "you'll be frozen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.7,
    "endTime": 68.635,
    "text": "Ha ha ha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.071,
    "endTime": 73.773,
    "text": "I have your back, Man of Spiders!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.773,
    "endTime": 75.408,
    "text": "My name is Spider-man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.408,
    "endTime": 76.376,
    "text": "That's what I said."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.376,
    "endTime": 77.911,
    "text": "Man of Spiders."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.911,
    "endTime": 79.145,
    "text": "Eh, yeah close enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.145,
    "endTime": 82.214,
    "text": "Oh, it appears the roller coaster is having"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.215,
    "endTime": 85.018,
    "text": "unexpected mechanical difficulties."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.587,
    "endTime": 88.988,
    "text": "The safety rules for this rescue:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.988,
    "endTime": 90.79,
    "text": "Don't be scared and hold on tight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.725,
    "endTime": 93.559,
    "text": "Ha ha ha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.56,
    "endTime": 95.061,
    "text": "Loki is wide open,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.061,
    "endTime": 96.83000000000001,
    "text": "but that man is in danger!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.83,
    "endTime": 98.064,
    "text": "I must save him!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.064,
    "endTime": 98.764,
    "text": "[zap]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.765,
    "endTime": 100.6,
    "text": "[clattering]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.6,
    "endTime": 101.734,
    "text": "[evil laugh]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.734,
    "endTime": 102.601,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.17,
    "endTime": 105.405,
    "text": "You may have stopped me here,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.405,
    "endTime": 107.307,
    "text": "but I have a backup plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.307,
    "endTime": 109.809,
    "text": "One that will make it cold and miserable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.809,
    "endTime": 111.945,
    "text": "for everyone, forever!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.945,
    "endTime": 113.113,
    "text": "[evil laugh]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.947,
    "endTime": 115.44800000000001,
    "text": "Shouldn't we help the hot dog vendor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.448,
    "endTime": 116.716,
    "text": "after we stop Loki?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.716,
    "endTime": 119.55099999999999,
    "text": "We will find Loki once we help the man of hot dogs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.552,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "[smashing ice]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 123.59,
    "text": "[distant laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.59,
    "endTime": 127.994,
    "text": "Now watch as my frost giant destroys summer fun forever!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.83,
    "endTime": 131.89800000000002,
    "text": "[smash]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.898,
    "endTime": 132.899,
    "text": "[roar]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.899,
    "endTime": 133.833,
    "text": "[scream]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.833,
    "endTime": 137.971,
    "text": "♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.971,
    "endTime": 139.506,
    "text": "I will take that big one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.506,
    "endTime": 141.541,
    "text": "And I will take the not really small,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.541,
    "endTime": 142.876,
    "text": "but not really big one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.878,
    "endTime": 146.613,
    "text": "[grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.613,
    "endTime": 147.914,
    "text": "Have at thee!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.914,
    "endTime": 150.183,
    "text": "[zap]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.183,
    "endTime": 151.98399999999998,
    "text": "[roar]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.985,
    "endTime": 152.78500000000003,
    "text": "[boom]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.785,
    "endTime": 153.786,
    "text": "Ha ha ha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.786,
    "endTime": 155.688,
    "text": "What? Where did he go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.688,
    "endTime": 157.357,
    "text": "Can I borrow this? Thank you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.357,
    "endTime": 158.391,
    "text": "My magic!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.926,
    "endTime": 161.261,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.996,
    "endTime": 164.364,
    "text": "[roar]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.364,
    "endTime": 165.93200000000002,
    "text": "Hey, leave Thor alone!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.932,
    "endTime": 167.065,
    "text": "He's my best customer!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.066,
    "endTime": 168.234,
    "text": "♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.234,
    "endTime": 169.369,
    "text": "[roar]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.369,
    "endTime": 170.27,
    "text": "♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.27,
    "endTime": 172.43800000000002,
    "text": "[whoosh]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.873,
    "endTime": 177.477,
    "text": "[shouts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.477,
    "endTime": 178.811,
    "text": "[whoosh]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 183.95,
    "text": "Ah! I love a sunny day and a super-hero ending."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.95,
    "endTime": 185.718,
    "text": "We could not have done it without you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.718,
    "endTime": 187.153,
    "text": "man of hot dogs. Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.153,
    "endTime": 190.256,
    "text": "Thank you. Hey, take a couple of veggie dogs..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.256,
    "endTime": 190.957,
    "text": "on the house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.727,
    "endTime": 197.697,
    "text": "We saved the day and defeated Loki, but first we made sure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.697,
    "endTime": 200.03300000000002,
    "text": "the ordinary folks were safe and sound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.033,
    "endTime": 202.702,
    "text": "Even if it's not as glamorous as stopping bad guys,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.702,
    "endTime": 204.837,
    "text": "it's always a good idea to keep an eye out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.837,
    "endTime": 205.804,
    "text": "for other people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.805,
    "endTime": 207.674,
    "text": "For me? Thank you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.674,
    "endTime": 208.241,
    "text": "Yum."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.674,
    "endTime": 208.241,
    "text": "Ah!"
  }
]